ny&rsquo;s <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://online.hmrc.gov.uk/corporation-tax/\" title=\"Corporation Tax online\"><abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> online account.</a> Allow 5 working days to process a Direct Debit the first time you set one up. After that, it’s 3 working days. Payments will appear on your bank statements as &ldquo;<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> NDDS&rdquo;.</p>\n\n<p>You can make changes to the Direct Debit through your company&rsquo;s <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> online account.</p>\n\n<h2>Online by debit or credit card</h2>\n\n<p>You can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.santanderbillpayment.co.uk/hmrc/scripts/nrpaynow.asp\" title=\"online payment service\">pay online.</a> You must have your Corporation Tax payment reference number. Allow 3 working days for payments to reach <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>.</p>\n\n<p>You must use a card issued by a UK card issuer - not American Express or Diners Club. </p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>There’s a 1.4% fee if you pay by credit card.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>At your bank or building society</h2>\n\n<p>Use your payslip to pay at your own bank by cash or cheque made payable to &lsquo;HM Revenue &amp; Customs only&rsquo; followed by your Corporation Tax payment reference number. Allow 3 working days for payments to reach <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>.</p>\n\n<h2>Post Office</h2>\n\n<p>You must use your payslip. You can pay by debit card, cash or cheque made payable to &lsquo;Post Office Ltd&rsquo;. Allow 3 working days for payments to reach <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>.</p>\n\n<h2>Nothing to pay</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> if you have <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/payinghmrc/ct-nil.htm\" title=\"No Corporation Tax payment due\">nothing to pay.</a></p>\n\n<h2>Payments for more than 1 company</h2>\n\n<p>If companies in a group pay under a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/ct/managing/pay-repay/group-pay.htm\" title=\"Group Payment Arrangements for Corporation Tax,\">Group Payment Arrangement</a> <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> will write telling you the correct payment reference. Contact <abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> if you don&rsquo;t have a reference. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> Group Payment Arrangement</strong><br />\n01236 785499</p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[{"title":"Running a limited company","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Flimited-company.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes registering, setting up, company accounts and tax returns","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Flimited-company","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/limited-company"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including help if you're self employed or a sole trader.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Business tax","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Fbusiness-tax.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes Corporation Tax, Self Assessment, Capital Gains Tax and VAT","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Fbusiness-tax","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/business-tax"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web